Grab your water balloons and jump into the
trash-filled world of H.U.R.L., a 3-D, first
person action game for "Baby DOOMers" of all
ages. You're a squeaky clean agent hot on the
trail of Bob the Slob and his Hardcore Union
of Radical Litterbugs, who'd love to bury you
under a mountain of slime. Earn money by
clearing trash, and then use the money to buy
soap, water balloons and deodorant. Shareware
version 1.0 from Millennium Media Group.